- You're back. 
 - You're back, Dr. Xu.

6
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,706
Dr. Xu, you were impressive today.

7
00:01:56,706 --> 00:01:58,195
You saved someone whose heart had stopped.

8
00:01:58,195 --> 00:02:00,362
I was just doing my job.

9
00:02:02,325 --> 00:02:04,925
The family members of the patient kept thanking you.

10
00:02:04,925 --> 00:02:07,046
Do you feel a sense of accomplishment being a doctor now?

11
00:02:07,046 --> 00:02:10,245
Don't you find the gratitude from the family touching?

12
00:02:11,306 --> 00:02:13,100
They will soon forget.

13
00:02:13,100 --> 00:02:14,168
Why would they?

14
00:02:14,168 --> 00:02:17,846
If a police officer saved you, would you forget about them quickly too?

15
00:02:34,119 --> 00:02:35,455
I would.

16
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:38,592
Humans are forgetful creatures by nature.

17
00:02:38,592 --> 00:02:43,071
Have you ever seen a patient come back to thank their doctor after going home?

18
00:02:48,068 --> 00:02:50,209
She's such a weirdo.

19
00:02:53,707 --> 00:02:54,820
Bye bye, Dr. Xu.

20
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:57,039
 - Bye, Dr. Xu. 
 - Bye bye.  

21
00:02:58,685 --> 00:03:01,848
Actually, I think being thanked once at that time should be enough.

22
00:03:01,848 --> 00:03:06,787
Besides, don't you feel proud when patients and their families express their gratitude?

23
00:03:06,787 --> 00:03:10,586
For me, treating patients and saving lives is just my duty.

24
00:03:10,586 --> 00:03:13,166
So you think this is merely fulfilling your duty

25
00:03:13,166 --> 00:03:15,285
and you don't need others' gratitude.

26
00:03:17,105 --> 00:03:21,145
I find your attitude quite unique.

27
00:03:21,968 --> 00:03:25,040
Whether or not the patients feel grateful is their choice,

28
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:27,207
and it doesn't affect my attitude.

29
00:03:27,207 --> 00:03:29,943
Medicine as a scientific field has its limitations.

30
00:03:29,943 --> 00:03:33,380
If a patient's condition goes beyond the limits of medicine,

31
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:35,766
even the most skilled doctor can't do anything.

32
00:03:35,766 --> 00:03:38,398
We are just ordinary people. We have no superpowers.

33
00:03:38,398 --> 00:03:40,013
That's the reality.

34
00:03:41,021 --> 00:03:42,556
Dr. Xu,

35
00:03:42,556 --> 00:03:45,359
you really are an unlikable doctor.

36
00:03:45,359 --> 00:03:48,528
We already have a likable doctor like you in our hospital, Dr. Yang.

37
00:03:48,528 --> 00:03:49,818
We don't need one more like me.

38
00:03:49,818 --> 00:03:52,199
Xu Qin, what does that mean?

39
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,679
Are you mocking me?

40
00:03:53,679 --> 00:03:55,999
I genuinely meant it as a compliment.

41
00:04:05,279 --> 00:04:06,879
What are you doing here?

42
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,215
I'm busy as hell here.

43
00:04:08,215 --> 00:04:10,150
I missed you.

44
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:12,759
I was nearby, so I'm paying you a visit.

45
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,421
As if.

46
00:04:14,421 --> 00:04:17,057
I mean it. It's been a few days since I saw you. And I missed you.

47
00:04:17,057 --> 00:04:18,358
I want to talk to you.

48
00:04:18,358 --> 00:04:20,825
I don't have time. Go somewhere else.

49
00:04:22,596 --> 00:04:23,997
I really need to talk to you.

50
00:04:23,997 --> 00:04:25,959
I need a favor.

51
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,605
What favor do you need from me?

52
00:04:27,605 --> 00:04:29,403
I'm working on a project recently.

53
00:04:29,403 --> 00:04:31,356
I wanted to ask you to invest in it.

54
00:04:33,912 --> 00:04:35,576
Are you mocking me?

55
00:04:35,576 --> 00:04:37,549
Don't you have money yourself?

56
00:04:38,745 --> 00:04:40,647
I'll be honest with you.

57
00:04:40,647 --> 00:04:44,218
The thing is, I'm doing this for my ex-girlfriend, Zhan Xiao Yao.

58
00:04:44,218 --> 00:04:45,585
As you know,

59
00:04:45,585 --> 00:04:48,512
she hasn't been doing anything these past couple of years.

60
00:04:48,512 --> 00:04:49,790
So I thought...

61
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:53,420
So you want to use me as an excuse?

62
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:54,995
Come on, don't put it like that.

63
00:04:54,995 --> 00:04:57,023
You're a big investor, right?

64
00:04:57,023 --> 00:04:59,879
Just let a little profit slip through your fingers to us.

65
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:04,300
Besides, I thought it would be fun for a few of us to do something together.

66
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:06,240
Wouldn't it be great?

67
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:09,733
The money that she needs, I can lend it to her personally.

68
00:05:09,733 --> 00:05:11,178
Leave me out of your project.

69
00:05:11,178 --> 00:05:14,246
I'm not interested in small projects like this.

70
00:05:14,853 --> 00:05:17,484
- You... 
 - I have some work to attend to.

71
00:05:17,484 --> 00:05:18,884
You should go.

72
00:05:19,753 --> 00:05:21,279
I'm going to finish my tea first.

73
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:23,113
Finish it alone then.

74
00:05:31,832 --> 00:05:33,773
Recently, Qin'er has been...

75
00:05:35,936 --> 00:05:39,066
If you have something to say, just spit it out, otherwise leave.

76
00:05:44,745 --> 00:05:47,147
Weren't you just saying that you're busy?

77
00:05:47,147 --> 00:05:49,067
Now you suddenly have time?

78
00:05:53,353 --> 00:05:55,322
She met with Song Yan.

79
00:05:55,322 --> 00:05:59,039
Aren't you afraid that they would get back together?

80
00:05:59,039 --> 00:06:01,020
She won't.

81
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:02,620
Right.

82
00:06:03,330 --> 00:06:05,859
With Auntie Fu pressing down on her like a mountain,

83
00:06:05,859 --> 00:06:08,446
she can only suppress herself more and more.

84
00:06:08,446 --> 00:06:12,377
That's why I'm worried about her mental well-being.

85
00:06:13,078 --> 00:06:15,179
I think Qin Qin is doing fine.

86
00:06:16,009 --> 00:06:18,279
That's according to your standards.

87
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:21,573
The way I see it, you also have issues.

88
00:06:22,616 --> 00:06:26,053
Both of you are living an unhappy life.

89
00:06:26,887 --> 00:06:28,173
And there's nothing you can do about it.

90
00:06:28,173 --> 00:06:30,566
You have such a mother, after all.

91
00:06:30,566 --> 00:06:33,727
I mean, look at you young people,

92
00:06:33,727 --> 00:06:37,360
you have everything, but you just can't live happily.

93
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,633
It's always cloudy and gloomy.

94
00:06:39,633 --> 00:06:41,933
What's the point?

95
00:06:51,378 --> 00:06:55,140
Qin'er hasn't had any friends since she came back.

96
00:06:55,140 --> 00:06:57,399
She's all alone.

97
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:59,319
Our girl has grown up.

98
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:02,980
She doesn't have any heart-to-heart talks with me anymore.

99
00:07:03,659 --> 00:07:06,784
And of course, she never shared them with you, either.

100
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:11,197
Tonight, invite her to my place for a drink.

101
00:07:11,197 --> 00:07:13,099
I'll also invite Xiao Yao.

102
00:07:13,099 --> 00:07:16,236
Introduce them to each other. Let them be friends.

103
00:07:16,236 --> 00:07:18,227
Their personalities are too different.

104
00:07:18,227 --> 00:07:20,173
They can't become friends.

105
00:07:20,173 --> 00:07:24,845
The greater the differences, the more likely they can become good friends.

106
00:07:24,845 --> 00:07:26,913
Do you want to bet on it?

107
00:07:26,913 --> 00:07:29,149
- What a waste of time. 
 - I'm being serious.

108
00:07:29,149 --> 00:07:30,959
I mean, look at us.

109
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:33,787
Haven't we been friends for so long?

110
00:07:33,787 --> 00:07:36,173
Why? Do you have a problem with this?

111
00:07:36,173 --> 00:07:37,599
It's not that.

112
00:07:37,599 --> 00:07:40,680
But you talk too much nonsense, and it's hurting my ears.

113
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,180
Just go.

114
00:07:45,866 --> 00:07:47,266
All right.

115
00:07:55,981 --> 00:07:57,079
Cheer up.

116
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:58,478
Be good to yourself.

117
00:07:58,478 --> 00:08:00,424
Otherwise, I'll feel sorry for you.

118
00:09:24,998 --> 00:09:26,466
Allow me to introduce.

119
00:09:26,466 --> 00:09:27,801
Qin'er.

120
00:09:27,801 --> 00:09:29,836
This is Xu Qin, my sister.

121
00:09:29,836 --> 00:09:32,519
This is Zhan Xiaoyao, my ex-girlfriend.

122
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:34,041
Hello.

123
00:09:34,041 --> 00:09:35,441
Hello.

124
00:09:36,884 --> 00:09:38,284
Brother.

125
00:09:40,239 --> 00:09:41,682
You two really are siblings.

126
00:09:41,682 --> 00:09:43,726
You are both aloof and quiet.

127
00:09:49,256 --> 00:09:51,559
I can't stand your OCD. 
  (T/N: Obsessive-compulsive disorder) 

128
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:53,326
Are your eyes microscopes?

129
00:09:53,326 --> 00:09:55,695
Everything seems dirty to you, huh?

130
00:09:55,695 --> 00:09:57,864
- Mind your own business. 
 - You're quite a character.

131
00:09:57,864 --> 00:10:00,439
Xiao Yixiao, you're always poking your nose into others' affairs.

132
00:10:00,439 --> 00:10:02,165
You can't tell me what to do.

133
00:10:02,899 --> 00:10:04,070
Where's your new boyfriend?

134
00:10:04,070 --> 00:10:05,605
Bring him over and let me check on him for you.

135
00:10:05,605 --> 00:10:07,807
I didn't see you bringing your girlfriend either.

136
00:10:07,807 --> 00:10:10,389
- We broke up. 
 - Congratulations.

137
00:10:12,346 --> 00:10:13,946
Get us a glass.

138
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:25,539
Xu Qin, do you have a boyfriend?

139
00:10:25,539 --> 00:10:26,727
I don't.

140
00:10:26,727 --> 00:10:29,329
You have to get one. Don't be like Meng Yanchen.

141
00:10:29,329 --> 00:10:31,653
Every time I see him, I think he's about to become a monk.

142
00:10:31,653 --> 00:10:34,234
I'm afraid I'll have to visit him at the temple next time.

143
00:10:34,234 --> 00:10:37,639
Director Zhan, return the investment fund to me.

144
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:41,975
Meng Yanchen is like a god among mortals. No one in this world is worthy of you.

145
00:10:41,975 --> 00:10:44,039
Does that mean I don't have to repay that money now?

146
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:47,159
Xu Qin, how about we find a boyfriend right here today?

147
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:49,335
Don't corrupt my sister.

148
00:10:50,284 --> 00:10:52,352
Xu Qin.

149
00:10:52,352 --> 00:10:55,179
Here's to our first meeting. I'll bottom up. Be my guest.

150
00:11:04,864 --> 00:11:06,533
- I like you. 
 - Slow down.

151
00:11:06,533 --> 00:11:08,969
Can you handle your drinks? Don't get drunk right away.

152
00:11:08,969 --> 00:11:10,838
Or Meng Yachen is going to scold me.

153
00:11:10,838 --> 00:11:12,879
I don't think you can outdrink me.

154
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:14,879
Well, let's find out about that today.

155
00:11:14,879 --> 00:11:16,279
Xiao Yixiao.

156
00:11:17,971 --> 00:11:19,413
Bring us shot glasses.

157
00:11:19,413 --> 00:11:20,813
Yes, Sir.

158
00:11:30,046 --> 00:11:32,058
- You girls are really doing this? 
 - Of course.

159
00:11:32,058 --> 00:11:34,494
- All right. Here. 
 - We will start first.

160
00:11:35,639 --> 00:11:37,039
Take it slow.

161
00:11:42,302 --> 00:11:43,600
Easy, girls.

162
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,000
 Xiao Yixiao, stop pulling me. 

163
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:47,519
- I'm not drunk. 
 - You are unbelievable.

164
00:11:47,519 --> 00:11:48,842
Why didn't you stop if you knew you couldn't handle it?

165
00:11:48,842 --> 00:11:50,810
- You're an adult. 
 - How could I possibly lose? 
    

166
00:11:50,810 --> 00:11:53,280
- Zhan Xiaorao, when it comes to embarrassing yourself, no one can beat you. 
 - How could I've lost?

167
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,815
You lost.

168
00:11:54,815 --> 00:11:57,054
No, I didn't, Xu Qin. Let's keep drinking.

169
00:11:57,859 --> 00:11:58,879
Sit tight.

170
00:11:58,879 --> 00:12:00,353
My car is over there. I'll take her home.

171
00:12:00,353 --> 00:12:02,012
- Okay, I'll take this one home then. 
 - Xu Qin...

172
00:12:02,012 --> 00:12:04,039
I want to sleep with Xu Qin.

173
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:07,080
Get up. Listen, Zhan Xiaorao, you're now blacklisted at my bar.

174
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,529
Give me a hand.

175
00:12:08,529 --> 00:12:10,287
Xu Qin!

176
00:12:10,287 --> 00:12:13,159
I don't want to go back. I want to drink!

177
00:12:13,159 --> 00:12:14,600
 Just stay still. 

178
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,200
We're here.

179
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,700
Get in.

180
00:12:19,406 --> 00:12:20,706
Hold the bag.

181
00:12:27,033 --> 00:12:29,716
Excuse me. Is this your car?

182
00:12:29,716 --> 00:12:31,399
Yes. Why?

183
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:34,354
I scratched it by accident.

184
00:12:34,354 --> 00:12:35,754
Where?

185
00:12:38,625 --> 00:12:40,727
- It's okay. 
 - Sorry?

186
00:12:40,727 --> 00:12:42,460
No need to pay for the damage.

187
00:15:17,151 --> 00:15:21,399
 Auntie and I are here to pick you up. 

188
00:15:21,399 --> 00:15:23,624
 And Brother Yanchen too. 

189
00:15:23,624 --> 00:15:26,065
 We are taking you home. 

190
00:15:36,639 --> 00:15:38,720
 Yanchen, 

191
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,579
 stay here with your sister. 

192
00:15:40,579 --> 00:15:42,959
 - Okay. 
 - We'll be right back. 

193
00:15:53,587 --> 00:15:55,287
 Qin Qin, 

194
00:15:56,672 --> 00:15:58,672
 I'm your brother. 

195
00:16:05,838 --> 00:16:08,385
 Qin Qin, I like cleanliness. 

196
00:16:08,385 --> 00:16:09,845
 This is too dirty. 

197
00:16:09,845 --> 00:16:11,279
 Let's throw it away. 

198
00:16:11,279 --> 00:16:12,779
 Let's get rid of it. 

199
00:16:21,919 --> 00:16:23,679
 It's so dirty. 

200
00:16:23,679 --> 00:16:25,399
 Look. 

201
00:16:25,399 --> 00:16:28,200
 Your fingernails are all black. 

202
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:30,256
 I am Meng Huaijin, Xu Haishan's comrade. 
  

203
00:16:30,256 --> 00:16:32,458
 This is my wife, Fu Wenying. 

204
00:16:32,458 --> 00:16:35,229
 The Civil Affairs Bureau is working on our adoption procedures. 

205
00:16:35,229 --> 00:16:38,123
 We are taking the child home today. 

206
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:50,060
 How did you... 

207
00:16:50,060 --> 00:16:51,399
 Yanchen. 

208
00:16:51,399 --> 00:16:53,539
 - Let's go. 
 - Okay. 

209
00:16:55,481 --> 00:16:56,981
 Come on. 

210
00:17:18,305 --> 00:17:20,026
You're up.

211
00:17:20,026 --> 00:17:22,346
Brother, you slept here last night?

212
00:17:24,232 --> 00:17:26,213
I cooked the dumplings in your fridge.

213
00:17:26,213 --> 00:17:27,913
Eat while they're warm.

214
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:34,520
Try them.

215
00:17:40,159 --> 00:17:43,666
The shrimp are quite big. It probably wrapped the whole thing.

216
00:17:44,985 --> 00:17:47,701
That's why I love eating this. It really is good.

217
00:17:47,701 --> 00:17:52,439
I didn't expect you would get along so well with Zhan Xiaorao.

218
00:17:52,439 --> 00:17:54,630
She's very likable.

219
00:17:55,500 --> 00:17:57,200
So are you.

220
00:18:03,699 --> 00:18:05,599
I'm annoying...

221
00:18:06,418 --> 00:18:08,418
and unlikable.

222
00:18:09,723 --> 00:18:12,967
Qin Qin, don't say that.

223
00:18:14,979 --> 00:18:17,285
I tried to reconcile with Song Yan,

224
00:18:19,607 --> 00:18:21,488
but he turned me down.

225
00:18:29,013 --> 00:18:30,713
Actually,

226
00:18:32,145 --> 00:18:34,352
it's better that he did.

227
00:18:35,449 --> 00:18:37,548
If he had agreed,

228
00:18:38,853 --> 00:18:41,352
I wouldn't know what to do.

229
00:18:43,624 --> 00:18:46,624
I don't even dare to tell Mom.

230
00:18:49,727 --> 00:18:52,066
He must have realized it, too.

231
00:18:53,126 --> 00:18:54,870
I wasn't resolute,

232
00:18:57,813 --> 00:18:59,812
so he detested me.

233
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:04,419
I must have looked ugly at that time.

234
00:19:06,379 --> 00:19:08,079
Brother,

235
00:19:08,079 --> 00:19:11,749
after I went abroad, did he ever write me a letter?

236
00:19:19,179 --> 00:19:20,679
It's okay.

237
00:19:33,307 --> 00:19:34,875
Keep eating.

238
00:19:34,875 --> 00:19:36,475
It's getting cold.

239
00:19:41,452 --> 00:19:43,392
Mom knows it's your day off.

240
00:19:44,185 --> 00:19:46,365
She asked me to tell you to go home.

241
00:19:49,371 --> 00:19:50,871
Got it.

242
00:20:29,862 --> 00:20:31,464
Take a 20-minute break right here.

243
00:20:31,464 --> 00:20:33,873
Next up, rope climbing.

244
00:20:36,075 --> 00:20:38,172
The break time in between is too short.

245
00:20:38,172 --> 00:20:39,920
Let them rest a little longer.

246
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:41,999
Ten minutes.

247
00:20:41,999 --> 00:20:43,199
Ten...

248
00:20:48,894 --> 00:20:52,640
When parents argue, the ones who suffer are the unlucky children.

249
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:56,319
Just shut up. You know very well why they are fighting.

250
00:20:56,319 --> 00:20:58,319
Have some water.

251
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:48,338
 Hi, is there anyone home in 1101? 

252
00:21:48,338 --> 00:21:50,238
 We are firefighters. 

253
00:21:51,645 --> 00:21:53,145
Coming!

254
00:22:08,562 --> 00:22:09,628
Hi, Miss Xu.

255
00:22:09,628 --> 00:22:12,031
They're from the firefighting force. The child from Unit 1201

256
00:22:12,031 --> 00:22:14,618
climbed out onto the balcony and got stuck in the air conditioning unit.

257
00:22:14,618 --> 00:22:15,925
His parents aren't home.

258
00:22:15,925 --> 00:22:17,926
Can we borrow your balcony?

259
00:22:18,839 --> 00:22:20,339
Please come in.

260
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,919
Old Jiang, put on the gear.

261
00:22:46,667 --> 00:22:48,860
Set up another safety pivot point.

262
00:22:53,359 --> 00:22:57,340
